  "title": "English Language Preschool Teacher",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Work with children aged 18 months to 6 years old</li><li>Conduct lessons with children in accordance to company's and ECDA's policies, guidelines and framework</li><li>Undertake operational and administrative duties for the centre to ensure compliance to industry regulations and smooth-running</li><li>Create a safe and enriching learning environment for children</li><li>Conduct routine care for children, keep accurate records of children's progress</li><li>Evaluate lesson plans</li><li>Communicate with parents on the progress of children development</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Fresh graduates welcome! Training is provided</li></ul>",
